{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, the achievable communication rate [128][129][130] and energy efficiency [131][132][133] are widely used to evaluate the communication performance.",
    "For example, He et al. [128] maximized the sum achievable rate of ISAC by jointly designing the transmit and receive beamforming.",
    "Moreover, He et al. [131] maximized the energy efficiency of ISAC by optimizing the transmit beamforming while satisfying the sensing requirements.",
    "Fundamental performance tradeoffDue to the shared hardware and spectrum resource, characterizing the fundamental performance tradeoff of the two functionalities is an important topic of ISAC, receiving significant research interest.",
    "There have been some recent studies that focus on the fundamental performance tradeoff from the perspective of information theory [134][135][136]."
  ]
}